        "created_at": "2025-08-05T14:18:58.573Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Define \u201cold-school\u201d. The most structured Faiveley vintages were made by Fran\u00e7ois, who ran the company between 1976 and 2004. This wine was (a) from before the era of Fran\u00e7ois and (b) a n\u00e9gociant wine likely purchased in barrel. So you might be extrapolating from cheese to chalk, as it were.</p>",
